WEBVTT

00:06.206 --> 00:07.274 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
GWEN IFILL: Good
evening. I'm Gwen Ifill.

00:07.274 --> 00:09.476 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And
I'm Judy Woodruff.

00:09.476 --> 00:13.680 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: On the "NewsHour"
tonight: Nearly 200 countries
make history with a breakthrough

00:13.680 --> 00:17.217 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
climate agreement.
What happens next?

00:17.217 --> 00:22.422 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
